						               													<description>A long time ago, two half-serving wizards lived in the depths of an old forest. The two were in training, but one day they were called by their master.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;I will test you from now on. Let's recognize the person who completed&amp;quot; Magical Remedy &amp;quot;first as a full-fledged wizard.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In order to make &amp;quot;magical remedies&amp;quot;, plants and minerals, parts of the body of animals and phantom beasts, and &amp;quot;fire (red)&amp;quot; &amp;quot;water (blue)&amp;quot; &amp;quot;earth (yellow)&amp;quot; &amp;quot;trees (green)&amp;quot; You must synthesize &amp;quot;rune stone&amp;quot; that has the magical power of &amp;quot;mineral (white)&amp;quot;. You will be one of the wizards and collect medicine materials in the fantasy forest. Then extract the magical power from the &amp;quot;rune stone&amp;quot; and complete the medicine faster than your rivals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, players take all stones of the same color on either the magic circle card or the center of the table and place them on the icon in their hand. Points will be deducted for stones that cannot be placed or surplus stones. When the stones are buried on the 5 icons in your hand, the card is complete. Get the score written on the card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you do not meet the end-of-game conditions, replenish the magic circle card with rune stones and perform the next round. In this way, the player who gets 30 points first is recognized as a full-fledged wizard by the master.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
